org.phoenixbioinformatics.api.db.api

Interface IPartner

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<com.poesys.db.dto.IDbDto>, com.poesys.db.dto.IDbDto, com.poesys.db.dto.IObserver, com.poesys.db.dto.ISubject, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractPartner, AbstractPartnerProxy, Partner, PartnerProxy

    public interface IPartner
extends com.poesys.db.dto.IDbDto

    A data-access layer data-transfer-object interface for the Partner. The data-transfer-object class and proxy class implement this interface, as does the business-layer data-transfer-object class.

    a system that comprises a unit for subscription, authentication, and authorization

    Stereotypes:

    • Persistent
    • SequenceKey

    Class is read/write: true

    Author:
    Poesys/DB Cartridge
